high_descs: Turn around to the table, turn left and head to the sink.
Pick up the tomato in the sink.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the toaster on the right counter.
Put the tomato on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the kitchen island, then turn left and move forward to go to the sink up ahead.
Pick up the tomato from in the sink.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside and heat it up, then take the tomato out.
Turn around and go forward to the counter, then turn right to face the counter above the dishwasher.
Put the tomato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right then head to the sink
Pick up the tomato in the sink
Open the microwave heat up the tomato then take it out and close the microwave
Turn left then face right on the counter with toaster
Put the tomato in front of the toaster on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the heated tomato on the counter
